      <title>特朗普希望总统对利率有发言权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/trump-wants-presidents-to-have-some-say-over-fed-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普表示，总统应该对利率和货币政策有一定的发言权，此举违背了美联储长期以来独立于政治参与者的惯例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/trump-wants-presidents-to-have-some-say-over-fed-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 19:22:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉因与奥尔特加发生争执将驱逐尼加拉瓜大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/lula-to-expel-nicaraguan-ambassador-amid-dispute-with-ortega</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦将驱逐尼加拉瓜驻巴西大使，这将加深这位左翼领导人与传统盟友丹尼尔·奥尔特加之间的裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/lula-to-expel-nicaraguan-ambassador-amid-dispute-with-ortega</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 19:13:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
